entry.title: This week's #DearSchuyler brings you a vulnerable, striking, and deeply compassionate conversation with consultant and educator, @Addison Rose Vincent 🙏🏼 I've listened to this episode a few times now and every time I do, I learn something new from Addison
entry.content: This week's #DearSchuyler brings you a vulnerable, striking, and deeply compassionate conversation with consultant and educator, @Addison Rose Vincent 🙏🏼 I've listened to this episode a few times now and every time I do, I learn something new from Addison. I reflect a little deeper. I challenge my own internalized transphobia. I'm so grateful for all Addison has offered us. Take a listen wherever you get your podcasts 💕 #transgender #trans #podcast
